Description: Native Linux Mod Manager inspired by Mod Organizer 2
 Anvil Organizer is a native Linux mod manager for games like Skyrim,
 Fallout 4, Cyberpunk 2077, Baldur's Gate 3, Starfield, and more.
 .
 Features include virtual file system deployment, profile management,
 Nexus Mods integration, drag-and-drop load ordering, and plugin
 conflict detection.
